                     <list>
                        <item xml:id="a1">
                           <locus target="#122vb">Fol. 122vb</locus>: Ownership note.<q xml:lang="gez">Fol. 122vb: ዝንቱ፡ መጽሐፍ፡ ዘቅዱስ፡ ሚካኤል፡ ዘቀርን፡ ሰበር፡ ዘተሣየጥዋ፡ በንዋየ፡ ቤተክርስቲያን፡ ወስዩመ፡ ሀገር፡ ወልደ፡ ሚካኤል፡፡ ወቄስ፡ ገበዙ፡ ክብረ፡ አብ፡ ዘአጽሐፍወ[sic]፡ ፬ደቂቀ፡ ሀብተ፡ ጽዮን፡፡ ዘሠረቆ፡ ወዘፈሐቆ፡ ለዝንቱ፡ መጽሐፍ፡ ውጉዘ፡ ለይኩን፡ በሥልጣነ፡ ጴጥሮስ፡ ወጳውሎስ፡፡ ወዓዲ፡ በቃለ፡ ፫፻፲ወ፰ርቱዓነ፡ ሃይማኖት፡ ለዓለመ፡ ዓለም፡ አሜን፡ ወአሜን፡ ለይኩን፡ ለይኩን፡፡ </q>
                           <q xml:lang="en"/>
                           The note mentions St. Michael of Qärn Säbär as the owner. It also indicates that the Ms. was bought with “the money of the church” and was commissioned “by four children of Habtä Ṣǝyon”.
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="e1">- Corrections written interlineally: fols. 10rb, 19vb, 21va, 26rb, 27va, 34vb, 42rb, 49va, 50vb, 52ra, 80ra, 80vb, 82va, 104rb, 120rb.&#xD;
- Space for rubricated names left unfilled: fols. 23va, 72vb, 88ra, 101rb.&#xD;
- The scribe used compressed script: fols. 27vb-28ra, 45va-vb, 49vb-50ra, 51va-vb, 57rb, 58vb-59ra, 61va-vb, 117ra-va, 123ra-124va.&#xD;
- The word እገሌ is marked by thin lines above and below on fols. e.g., 28ra, 29rb, 40va, 72va-vb, 73ra-rb.&#xD;
- Minor notes and writing exercises: fols. 1v, 11v, 86v, 87r, 95v.</item>
